            "Jesahel"  is a song by the Italian progressive rock band Delirium, released as a single in 1972. It was written by Oscar Prudente e Ivano Fossati. Ivano Alberto Fossati (born September 21, 1951) is an Italian pop singer-songwriter, guitarist, pianist, and percussionist born in Genoa.
